posts.title: Prayer Request for my son. I am reaching out so I don't have to walk this alone and call upon help to heal.
posts.content:
Please pray with me. My son is on life support from a failed heart. He had emergency surgery late last night and given a 5% chance, now in ICU on life support. His pulse stopped several times, his heart massaged and he was opened up for heart surgery. He is being kept in a coma 34, vax'd, no boosters.

My husband was with him, they had just played a game of Backgammin and finished watching Severance together, best friends. I said goodnight, I love you, and he went to lay down when his pain started, with no warning, dad called 911.

"Bless the Lord, O my soul, and forget not all his benefits, who forgives all your iniquity, who heals all your diseases, who redeems your life from the pit, who crowns you with steadfast love and mercy" ~ Psalm 103:2-4

Lord Jesus, thank you that you love my son DJ. I know that you hate what his illness is doing to him. I ask, in the name of Jesus, that you would heal him, that you would have compassion and bring healing from all sickness. You know he has always been a loving, caring, compassionate son, teacher, healer and friend to all, the best son a mother could have, a beautiful person.

O Lord Almighty, the Healer of our souls and bodies, You Who put down and raise up, Who chastise and also heal; in Your great mercy, visit our brother DJ, my son, who is on life support in the hospital.

Stretch forth Your hand that is full of healing and health, and raise him up from his bed, and cure him of his failed heart.

I lean fully on you Lord, for You alone are able. I love you; I need you this day, and always.

Thank you for praying with me Frens. May Jesus continue loving and blessing you always. Thank you all for being here together in goodness, love and grace. Going to be in solitude away a little bit I will update when I can. Amen

posts.title: Prayer Request for my son. I am reaching out so I don't have to walk this alone and call upon help to heal.
posts.content:
Please pray with me. My son is on life support from a failed heart. He had emergency surgery late last night and given a 5% chance, now in ICU on life support. His pulse stopped several times, his heart massaged and he was opened up for heart surgery. He is being kept in a coma 34, vax'd, no boosters.

My husband was with him, they had just played a game of Backgammin and finished watching Severance together, best friends. I said goodnight, I love you, and he went to lay down when his pain started, with no warning, dad called 911.

"Bless the Lord, O my soul, and forget not all his benefits, who forgives all your iniquity, who heals all your diseases, who redeems your life from the pit, who crowns you with steadfast love and mercy" ~ Psalm 103:2-4

Lord Jesus, thank you that you love my son DJ. I know that you hate what his illness is doing to him. I ask, in the name of Jesus, that you would heal him, that you would have compassion and bring healing from all sickness. You know he has always been a loving, caring, compassionate son, teacher, healer and friend to all, the best son a mother could have, a beautiful person.

O Lord Almighty, the Healer of our souls and bodies, You Who put down and raise up, Who chastise and also heal; in Your great mercy, visit our brother DJ, my son, who is on life support in the hospital.

Stretch forth Your hand that is full of healing and health, and raise him up from his bed, and cure him of his failed heart.

I lean fully on you Lord, for You alone are able. I love you; I need you this day, and always.

Thank you for praying with me Frens. May Jesus continue loving and blessing you always. Thank you all for being here together in goodness, love and grace. Going to be in solitude away a little bit I will update when I can. Amen

posts.title: Prayer Request for my son. I am reaching out so I don't have to walk this alone and call upon help to heal.
posts.content:
Please pray with me. My son is on life support from a failed heart. He had emergency surgery late last night and given a 5% chance, now in ICU on life support. His pulse stopped several times, his heart massaged and he was opened up for heart surgery. He is being kept in a coma 34, vax'd, no boosters.

My husband was with him, they had just played a game of Backgammin and finished watching Severance together, best friends. I said goodnight, I love you, and he went to lay down when his pain started, with no warning, dad called 911.

"Bless the Lord, O my soul, and forget not all his benefits, who forgives all your iniquity, who heals all your diseases, who redeems your life from the pit, who crowns you with steadfast love and mercy" ~ Psalm 103:2-4

Lord Jesus, thank you that you love my son DJ. I know that you hate what his illness is doing to him. I ask, in the name of Jesus, that you would heal him, that you would have compassion and bring healing from all sickness. You know he has always been a loving, caring, compassionate son, teacher, healer and friend to all, the best son a mother could have, a beautiful person.

O Lord Almighty, the Healer of our souls and bodies, You Who put down and raise up, Who chastise and also heal; in Your great mercy, visit our brother DJ, my son, who is on life support in the hospital.

Stretch forth Your hand that is full of healing and health, and raise him up from his bed, and cure him of his failed heart.

I lean fully on you Lord, for You alone are able. I love you; I need you this day, and always.

Thank you for praying with me Frens. May Jesus continue loving and blessing you always. Thank you all for being here together in goodness, love and grace. Going to be in solitude away a little bit I will update when I can. Amen

posts.title: Prayer Request for my son. I am reaching out so I don't have to walk this alone and call upon help to heal.
posts.content:
Please pray with me. My son is on life support from a failed heart. He had emergency surgery late last night and given a 5% chance, now in ICU on life support. His pulse stopped several times, his heart massaged and he was opened up for heart surgery. He is being kept in a coma 34, vax'd, no boosters.

My husband was with him, they had just played a game of Backgammin and finished watching Severance together, best friends. I said goodnight, I love you, and he went to lay down when his pain started, with no warning, dad called 911.

"Bless the Lord, O my soul, and forget not all his benefits, who forgives all your iniquity, who heals all your diseases, who redeems your life from the pit, who crowns you with steadfast love and mercy" ~ Psalm 103:2-4

Lord Jesus, thank you that you love my son DJ. I know that you hate what his illness is doing to him. I ask, in the name of Jesus, that you would heal him, that you would have compassion and bring healing from all sickness. You know he has always been a loving, caring, compassionate son, teacher, healer and friend to all, the best son a mother could have, a beautiful person.

O Lord Almighty, the Healer of our souls and bodies, You Who put down and raise up, Who chastise and also heal; in Your great mercy, visit our brother DJ, my son, who is on life support in the hospital.

Stretch forth Your hand that is full of healing and health, and raise him up from his bed, and cure him of his failed heart.

I lean fully on you Lord, for You alone are able. I love you; I need you this day, and always.

Thank you for praying with me Frens. May Jesus continue loving and blessing you always. Thank you all for being here together in goodness, love and grace. Going to be in solitude away a little bit I will update when I can. Amen

posts.title: Prayer Request for my son. I am reaching out so I don't have to walk this alone and call upon help to heal.
posts.content:
Please pray with me. My son is on life support from a failed heart. He had emergency surgery late last night and given a 5% chance, now in ICU on life support. His pulse stopped several times, his heart massaged and he was opened up for heart surgery. He is being kept in a coma 34, vax'd, no boosters.

My husband was with him, they had just played a game of Backgammin and finished watching Severance together, best friends. I said goodnight, I love you, and he went to lay down when his pain started, with no warning, dad called 911.

"Bless the Lord, O my soul, and forget not all his benefits, who forgives all your iniquity, who heals all your diseases, who redeems your life from the pit, who crowns you with steadfast love and mercy" ~ Psalm 103:2-4

Lord Jesus, thank you that you love my son DJ. I know that you hate what his illness is doing to him. I ask, in the name of Jesus, that you would heal him, that you would have compassion and bring healing from all sickness. You know he has always been a loving, caring, compassionate son, teacher, healer and friend to all, the best son a mother could have, a beautiful person.

O Lord Almighty, the Healer of our souls and bodies, You Who put down and raise up, Who chastise and also heal; in Your great mercy, visit our brother DJ, my son, who is on life support in the hospital.

Stretch forth Your hand that is full of healing and health, and raise him up from his bed, and cure him of his failed heart.

I lean fully on you Lord, for You alone are able. I love you; I need you this day, and always.

Thank you for praying with me Frens. May Jesus continue loving and blessing you always. Thank you all for being here together in goodness, love and grace. Going to be in solitude away a little bit I will update when I can. Amen

posts.title: Prayer Request for my son. I am reaching out so I don't have to walk this alone and call upon help to heal.
posts.content:
Please pray with me. My son is on life support from a failed heart. He had emergency surgery late last night and given a 5% chance, now in ICU on life support. His pulse stopped several times, his heart massaged and he was opened up for heart surgery. He is being kept in a coma 34, vax'd, no boosters.

My husband was with him, they had just played a game of Backgammin and finished watching Severance together, best friends. I said goodnight, I love you, and he went to lay down when his pain started, with no warning, dad called 911.

"Bless the Lord, O my soul, and forget not all his benefits, who forgives all your iniquity, who heals all your diseases, who redeems your life from the pit, who crowns you with steadfast love and mercy" ~ Psalm 103:2-4

Lord Jesus, thank you that you love my son DJ. I know that you hate what his illness is doing to him. I ask, in the name of Jesus, that you would heal him, that you would have compassion and bring healing from all sickness. You know he has always been a loving, caring, compassionate son, teacher, healer and friend to all, the best son a mother could have, a beautiful person.

O Lord Almighty, the Healer of our souls and bodies, You Who put down and raise up, Who chastise and also heal; in Your great mercy, visit our brother DJ, my son, who is on life support in the hospital.

Stretch forth Your hand that is full of healing and health, and raise him up from his bed, and cure him of his failed heart.

I lean fully on you Lord, for You alone are able. I love you; I need you this day, and always.

Thank you for praying with me Frens. May Jesus continue loving and blessing you always. Thank you all for being here together in goodness, love and grace. Going to be in solitude away a little bit I will update when I can. Amen
